{"tid":2146683,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"隔離台24小時內出到MV 廢祝楊明PASSING OUT","createTime":"2020-08-08T18:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T20:11:30.000Z","uid":45498,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b853cf0de600e1d69bca5ec80c50e78aca1416b6","tid":2146683,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T18:03:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdIn0fCpJ5A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAdIn0fCpJ5A&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=cd1f8f45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdIn0fCpJ5A</a><br />\n<br />\n#這是正式錄用的撐警成員嗎 #撐警就唔接受酒精呼氣測試都得 #楊明立萬好機會<br />\n【高登音樂台】漏奶 - 醉駕 ( 原曲：飛花 )<br />\n<br />\n醉駕<br />\n唱 ：漏奶<br />\n改詞 ：畢加索斯&amp;董折<br />\nMV ：漏奶<br />\n鳴謝：楊明架BENZ，佢條女，條路參與演出<br />\n<br />\n凌晨眼光光 <br />\n坐上車揸到爽<br />\n去到半山中 <br />\n陌生的地方<br />\n醉到眼矇矇 <br />\n見到許多欄杆<br />\n當佢冇野剷上壆才醒覺<br />\n<br />\n楊明技術很差 <br />\n卻仲要來酒駕<br />\n誰能求藍絲照著你<br />\n拉鳩你無閒話<br />\n楊明平治不差 <br />\n仍撞甩bumper散架<br />\n其實你演戲像那屎忽花<br />\n<br />\n為何流下淚 <br />\n醉駕這種前科<br />\n女友也擔心 <br />\n柒到炒路旁<br />\n楊明還在願望靠<br />\n撐警翻身無望<br />\n報應到了這次<br />\n卻像幻覺真不爽<br />\n<br />\n楊明技術很差 <br />\n卻仲要來酒駕<br />\n誰能求藍絲照著你<br />\n拉鳩你無閒話<br />\n楊明平治不差 <br />\n仍撞到bumper散架<br />\n其實你演戲像那屎忽花<br />\n<br />\n楊明技術很差 <br />\n卻仲要來酒駕<br />\n誰能求藍絲照著你<br />\n拉鳩你不說話<br />\n楊明平治不差 <br />\n仍撞到bumper散架<br />\n其實你演戲像那屎忽花<br />\n還望會攞到視帝真羞家"},{"pid":"687f9791aeb20f8453fab877cb5c0f946eec3f75","tid":2146683,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T18:04:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe28b7a9c4572bfc7dc1ab3c05fdc13398acc376","tid":2146683,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T18:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4687ccbbefda648694d4a7ebb1a74d3e4565df","tid":2146683,"uid